org.promasi.model
Class Employee

java.lang.Object
  org.promasi.model.Person
      org.promasi.model.Employee

public class Employee
extends Person

Represents an employee.(Developer,Tester,Designer etc). All the fields of the employee(experienced etc) have a range of 0.0-10.0

Author:
eddiefullmetal
